% Tag-driven routing in a distributed storage network
% Ximin Luo

A system for decentralised search.

## Build-depends

### Main

ant

python

git

### Docs

bliki-doclet
:	http://github.com/infinity0/bliki-doclet
:	Make sure the `.jar` exists at `doc/bliki-doclet.jar`

pandoc
:	http://johnmacfarlane.net/pandoc/
:	Debian: install `pandoc`

pdflatex
:	Debian: install `texlive-latex-base`

GNU coreutils
:	Debian: install `coreutils`

### Scraper

graph-easy (CPAN)
:	http://search.cpan.org/~tels/Graph-Easy/
:	Debian: install `dh-make-perl`, then run `cpan2deb Graph::Easy` to create a
	local `.deb` of `libgraph-easy-perl`, which you should then install.

JUNG
:	http://jung.sourceforge.net/

pydot
:	http://www.dkbza.org/pydot.html
:	Debian: install `python-pydot`

FlickrAPI
:	http://stuvel.eu/flickrapi/
:	Debian: install `python-flickrapi`
